  "description": "This individual is an undead of advanced decay, with taupe skin drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and a rigid, forward-set jaw. Gray eyes sit recessed in darkened sockets, fixed in an unblinking stare typical of hollow-wake revenants. Brown hair remains in sparse, uneven clumps, cut close by loss rather than design. The body carries a persistent glass-sheen of embedded particulate along the forearms and throat, a defining mark of prolonged exposure to the Hollow’s vitrified dust.",
